'''Domain Rapuung''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Though they were a warrior caste, the domain's most famous member was [[Vua Rapuung]], a [[Shamed Ones|Shamed One]] who fought alongside [[Anakin Solo]] on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] as he attempted to reclaim his former status. The skirmish that followed marked the beginning of the [[Jeedai heresy|Jedi Heresy]] that would ultimately prove devastating to the Vong war effort.<ref name="EoV1">''[[The New Jedi Order: Edge of Victory I: Conquest]]''</ref>

